==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Sworn
<hw>Sworn</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <def><pos>p. p.</pos> of
<er>Swear</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><cs><col><b>Sworn brothers</b></col>, <cd>originally, companions in
arms who took an oath to share together good and bad fortune; hence,
faithful friends.</cd> -- <col><b>Sworn enemies</b></col>,
<cd>determined or irreconcilable enemies.</cd> -- <col><b>Sworn
friends</b></col>, <cd>close friends.</cd></cs>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Swough</ent>⟦br⟧
